Flickr Helper

A CakePHP Library & Helper for displaying Flickr Photos

INSTALLATION
------------

Copy Flickr.php to your app/Vendor directory

Copy FlickrHelper.php to your app/View/Helper directory

CONFIGURATION
---------------

In FlickrHelper.php, update $_apiKey with your Flickr API Key

    protected $_apiKey = 'YOUR_FLICKR_API_KEY';

USAGE
---------------

The following examples demonstrate various uses in your view:

    echo $this->Flickr->photo(2973425255);

    echo $this->Flickr->photo(2973425255, 's');

    echo $this->Flickr->photo(2973425255, 'm', array('alt' => 'Aidan Love', 'class' => 'photo', 'height' => 200, 'width' => 300));

    echo $this->Flickr->url(2973425255);

